|-------------|-------------|----------------|
| **Educational Platforms** | Teaching media literacy with open implementations | ✅ Compliant |
| **News Organizations** | Building transparent verification workflows | ✅ Compliant |
| **Research Institutions** | Studying synthetic media with published methods | ✅ Compliant |
| **Privacy-Focused Browsers** | Integrating verification with user consent | ✅ Compliant |
| **Open Source Social Platforms** | Community-driven fact-checking tools | ✅ Compliant |

### ❌ Problematic Applications

| Application | Issue | Required Action |
|-------------|-------|----------------|
| **Surveillance Companies** | Using privacy tech for monitoring | 🚫 Violates mission |
| **Closed Platforms** | Proprietary content filtering | 📝 Must open source |
| **Manipulation Services** | Using detection to improve deception | 🚫 Violates mission |
| **Centralized Censorship** | Removing user agency and choice | 🚫 Violates mission |

