## 🏢 Enterprise & Commercial Options

### Open Source Path (Free)

* ✅ Full commercial use allowed
* ✅ Must open source modifications
* ✅ Must contribute improvements back
* ✅ Maintain community access

### Commercial License Path (Paid)

* ✅ Proprietary integration rights
* ✅ Custom enterprise features
* ✅ Priority support and consulting
* ✅ Protected intellectual property usage

### Partnership Principles

We welcome partnerships that align with our values:

* 🎯 **Mission Alignment** - Share our commitment to user empowerment
* 🔍 **Transparency** - Commercial uses should enhance trust
* 🤝 **Community Benefit** - Strengthen the open source ecosystem
* 🛡️ **Privacy Respect** - No surveillance or manipulation focus

